# Figma MCP UI Sync Mode / Figma 协作同步模式

- Trigger / 触发条件: when UI changes are requested and Figma MCP is available.
- Goal / 目标: keep implementation aligned with design intent while preserving project conventions.

## Required Workflow / 必须流程

1) Read design context first / 先读设计上下文
- Fetch node context from Figma MCP (fileKey + nodeId).
- Capture key constraints: spacing, typography, states, interaction notes.

2) Adapt to codebase / 工程化适配
- Reuse existing components/tokens/styles before creating new ones.
- Avoid direct pixel-perfect copy when it conflicts with accessibility or existing architecture.

3) Record design reference / 记录设计引用
- For each UI task, include `Design Ref` (Figma URL or node id) in task notes/todo.
- Document intentional deviations with short rationale.

4) Verify before done / 完成前验证
- Run impacted checks:
  - `pnpm --filter customer-web lint`
  - `pnpm --filter customer-web type-check`
  - `pnpm --filter customer-web build`
- Ensure loading/empty/error/disabled states are present for interactive UI.

## Guardrails / 护栏

- Do not introduce `any` for UI data contracts unless unavoidable and documented.
- Prefer semantic HTML and accessible labels/roles.
- Keep visual changes scoped; avoid unrelated refactors in same patch.
